<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Travel Bucket List</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #ff4b2b;
            --secondary-color: #ff416c;
            --text-color: #2c3e50;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff4b2b, #ff416c);
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 { color: var(--text-color); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        
        p { 
            color: #555; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .back-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff4b2b, #ff416c);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 75, 43, 0.4);
        }

        .feature-list {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About the Project 📂</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the <strong>Travel Bucket List</strong> application! This platform is designed to help you organize and manage your future travel destinations in one sleek directory.</p>
        
        <div class="feature-list">
            <strong>Key Features:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Dynamic List Management (using local arrays)</li>
                <li>Express.js Routing for multiple pages</li>
                <li>EJS Templating for a clean UI</li>
                <li>Responsive Design with modern CSS</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>Developed for the Express Routing and Templates assignment.</p>
        
        <a href="/" class="back-btn">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>